{
  "rationale": "To ensure systematic area coverage and safe, non-oscillatory wall-following, I introduce a helper state (wall_following) to distinguish between open exploration and wall-adjacent behavior. The supervisor always reacts safely to obstacles and never attempts forward movement into a blocked path.",
