  "coverage_strategy": [
    "Prioritize moving forward when the path is clear; otherwise, follow the wall on the left or right.",
    "Switch to wall_following after initiating forward motion next to a wall.",
    "Rotate away from obstacles when blocked in front, preferring to maintain wall contact.",
    "Use full_rotate only when completely blocked in front to escape dead-ends.",
    "Avoid oscillating between rotate actions by progressing to wall_following after forward movement.",
    "Encourage systematic coverage by re-entering exploration (clear) when path is open after wall-following."
